          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/96353311/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u96353311-27.jpg" alt="千江阅" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37296670/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37296670/" class="">第24页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/96353311/" class=" " title="千江阅">千江阅</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37296670">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">旧精英的衰落表现为人道主义和利他主义的增长，而新精英的兴起则表现为卑微之众对强大权威的报复。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-03-02 15:58</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                旧精英的衰落表现为人道主义和利他主义的增长，而新精英的兴起则表现为卑微之众对强大权威的报复。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37296670/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-03-02 15:58
                </div>
              </div>
